{"tid":1332554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解有人(廿幾至中年人士)做茄喱啡(冇對白)","createTime":"2019-07-19T10:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:42:12.000Z","uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9333b1c03e652efe1cb4765ae3ac2214032ac072","tid":1332554,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"放假無聊 朋友做廣告既 去幫下佢手 同啲演員傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 勁低人工 講緊400-500蚊全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 自問樣/身材/性格冇特別 居然發夢有日會發圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 冇對白 做背景 有人問到你做過乜 白紙一片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 廿幾個陣做茄喱啡 做左三四年仲做緊二打六(真係background行過)就應該接受現實 搵番份正當職業 <br />\n5. 最搞笑係 以上講緊個條友 居然同我地講點解搵XXX做女主角 覺得佢唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個女主角雖則唔係最出名 但都叫識做戲 有特色 面細細眼大大 白白淨靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係有咁多普通人做到明星咩？"},{"pid":"e7bc90fa19a3385562154eec7060391dc925b14a","tid":1332554,"uid":226616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"佢細個唔讀書"},{"pid":"172fe62fd482ae1d757b288bd8faf7ffa91a0fee","tid":1332554,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7bc90fa19a3385562154eec7060391dc925b14a","tid":1332554,"uid":226616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"佢細個唔讀書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"唔讀書都可以做好多正當工<br />\n<br />\n例子: 地盤/空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55983b9eba2c7f279ab98ed834a2eee2600e346","tid":1332554,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:42:12.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}